    "en": {
      "title": "Firing in Badula",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A firing has been conducted at the Hindagoda IOC fuel station located on the Badulai-Pasara main road.",
        "Due to a verbal dispute between the employee of the filling station and the person who came to collect the fuel, the person who came to collect the fuel fired a 9 mm gun towards the sky.",
        "Although no one was injured, the Padula police are proceeding to arrest the suspect."
      ],
